title: Departamentos (Mexico, 1836)
name: Departamentos (Mexico, 1836)
description:
Boundaries of departments in Mexico, 1836.

These are largely based on Commons, Gerhard and O'Gorman, and digitized boundaries of present-day states at a 1:1,000,000 scale.

There is a lot to improve on these datasets based on more detailed local studies and official cartography. Please report any error to the author. See citation URL for a list of sources used to prepare these maps.

Please cite if used (see citation in the sidebar)
